# CryptoWeather Nexus Environment Variables

# OpenWeatherMap API Key
# Get your API key from: https://openweathermap.org/api
NEXT_PUBLIC_OPENWEATHER_API_KEY=your_openweather_api_key_here

# NewsData.io API Key
# Get your API key from: https://newsdata.io/
NEXT_PUBLIC_NEWSDATA_API_KEY=your_newsdata_api_key_here

# Note: CoinCap API is free and doesn't require an API key for basic usage
# WebSocket endpoint: wss://ws.coincap.io/prices
# REST API endpoint: https://api.coincap.io/v2/

# Instructions:
# 1. Rename this file to .env.local
# 2. Replace the placeholder values with your actual API keys
# 3. Restart the development server after making changes
# 4. Never commit the actual .env.local file to version control